	    <img class="alignleft" width="100%"  alt="" src="<?php echo image_url('cedar/1936blizzard/1936Blizzard-3.jpg');?>">
	    <div class="vspacer"></div>
	    <div class="vspacer"></div>
		<p>The first two weeks of January were again rather mild, with six of those days above freezing. Five inches of snow did fall from the 4th to the 8th, but the high on the 14th was 43 degrees. It would be the last day above freezing until February 23rd. A storm on January 16th-17th dumped 5 inches of snow. The thermometer fell to -10 degrees on the 19th and registered below zero every morning until February 12th. </p>
